0.name: Inspiron™ 14 7000 Series
0.descp:
The new 14” Inspiron 7000 gives you the mobility you asked for – thinner, stronger, and more power, plus long battery life and an ultra-bright Full HD touch screen (optional). Your wish is our design.
Razor-thin design.  At just .6” thin, it’s sleeker, stronger and easier to carry.

1.name: Inspiron™ 15 7000 Series
1.descp:
The new 15” Inspiron 7000 gives you the multimedia you asked for – thinner, stronger and brighter, plus more power, graphics, and audio to take anywhere. Your wish is our design.A keyboard to count on
With a backlit keyboard and 10-key numeric keypad, you can type and crunch numbers anywhere, anytime.

2.name: Inspiron™ 11 3000 Series
2.descp: Meet the laptop that goes anywhere. With a touch screen that changes everything. So intuitive, so light, the sleek Inspiron 11 keeps you connected with a tap of the screen.

3.name: XPS™ 12 Convertible UltraBook™
3.descp: Meet the acclaimed XPS™ 12 with an innovative flip-hinge design to easily convert from laptop work to tablet fun. Tap-to-pair supported devices* and tap-to-share photos, files and more* with NFC (Near Field Communication). Thanks to its next gen Intel® 4th gen processors, you’re ready for more doing and less waiting.

4.name: XPS™ 13
4.descp: Enjoy the view from almost any angle with the new Dell™ XPS™ 13 Ultrabook™. Now with an optional full HD screen.

5.name: Inspiron™ 23 AIO Desktop
5.descp: Our thinnest all-in-one not only saves space, but turns heads with premium materials and impressive attention to detail.

6.name: Latitude™ 10
6.descp: Latitude™ 10 is the tablet that’s built for business with easy management and security, and a swappable battery for go-anywhere productivity.

7.name: Vostro™ 5470
7.descp: Work smarter and look sharp with the new Vostro 5470 14-inch Windows® 8 laptop.  With faster performance, touch screen option1, and the essential security and support you need to keep you on the winning path.

8.name: Inspiron™ 14
8.descp: Meet the laptop that handles the basics beautifully. So portable, so versatile, the Inspiron 14 is the perfect match for those who want everyday computing at a value.

9.name: Inspiron™ 14R
9.descp: Meet the laptop that’s easy to carry, yet so hard to put down. Stylish and perfect for games and movies, the Inspiron 14R lets you take entertainment on the go.

10.name: Inspiron™ 15
10.descp: More value. With an unexpected touch. Introducing the affordable new Inspiron™ 15. Featuring an optional touch screen that takes full advantage of Windows 8. Thin and light, and with an impressive battery life, this laptop keeps up with you on your busiest days.

11.name: Inspiron™ 15R
11.descp:
The new Inspiron 15R. It’s a touching story. With the new Inspiron™ 15R, your entertainment experience
just got better. Much better. Powered by the new, touch-friendly Windows 8, the Inspiron™ 15R features
stellar graphics on gorgeous touch screen that you can’t keep your fingers off of. Whether you’re
working or watching a show on the go, stay connected* and have more fun doing it.

12.name: XPS™ 11
12.descp: The new XPS 11 2-in-1 Ultrabook™ takes performance and design to the next level. Premium materials, such as carbon fiber and damage resistant Corning® Gorilla® Glass NBT™, maximize durability. The UltraSharp™ Quad HD display delivers stunning detail, and the solid surface backlit touch keyboard is designed to withstand tablet usage. New 4th generation Intel® Core™ processors power your work and play to the max. It’s time to experience beauty and unbridled innovation like never before.

13.name: XPS™ 15
13.descp: Dell celebrates the passion to create with the Dell XPS 15. A high-performance laptop with 4th gen Intel® Core ™ processors, Windows 8 Pro, a 15.6” optional UltraSharp™ QHD   touch display constructed of damage-resistant Corning® Gorilla® Glass NBTTM. We can’t wait to see what you do with it.
